snippet.textDisplay: 50 I am so happy for you. This is deeper than an award, this is a life battle against the odds. A life time of hard work, dedication and never giving in. You have helped me in my life, I have drawn from your hard work and determination growing up, and I am certain others have also. You are a very inspiring person and all the trolling of people aside and games, you are a great man or maybe the trolling and jokes make you greater lol. I am so glad that this has been 'officially' recognised and that you have some kind of satisfaction and peace from it. From watching this video I would say you do. Thank you for being there with out know so and providing great entertainment.  Peace OG.
